songs.title: On My Way
songs.lyrics:
[Hook]
Tu me vois partir dans un truck on my way home
Catch me sippin' in the bus on my way home
Catch me not giving a fuck on my way home
J'ai dépensé deux-mille bucks on my way home
Tu me vois partir dans un truck on my way home
Catch me sippin' in the bus on my way home
Catch me not giving a fuck on my way home

She don't give a fuck, she on her way home
J'men fous j'en ai déjà une à la maison
Well, j'en ai déjà 2 à la maison
Getting money done, did it on my way home
Straight cash just speedin' on my way home

Like, can you give me this
